306
00:14:31,160 --> 00:14:32,360
He's red-hot now.

307
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:33,760
Look at all those fans.

308
00:14:33,760 --> 00:14:35,200
They were probably with him
at the competition.

309
00:14:35,480 --> 00:14:38,840
The Hangzhou Asian Games
will have esports events.

310
00:14:46,400 --> 00:14:47,920
Cong, well done.

311
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:48,400
Go.

312
00:14:48,680 --> 00:14:50,080
Find a pen and paper,

313
00:14:50,280 --> 00:14:51,520
