314
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,640
Hurry.

315
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:54,520
Don't push.

316
00:14:54,520 --> 00:14:55,400
One at a time.

317
00:14:56,520 --> 00:14:57,920
Okay, that's all for today.

318
00:14:57,920 --> 00:14:59,200
We're running late. Until next time.

319
00:14:59,200 --> 00:14:59,840
Here.

320
00:15:11,000 --> 00:15:12,560
Pen and paper.

321
00:15:12,560 --> 00:15:13,160
Come on.

322
00:15:13,320 --> 00:15:13,680
What's going on?

323
00:15:13,680 --> 00:15:14,680
Larry's here.

324
00:15:14,880 --> 00:15:16,120
Which Larry?

325
00:15:16,360 --> 00:15:17,360
How many do you know?

326
00:15:17,360 --> 00:15:18,120
The Larry?

327
00:15:20,320 --> 00:15:22,000
Get me an autograph.

328
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:22,880
We need to check it.

329
00:15:24,720 --> 00:15:25,960
I was just joking, sir.

330
00:15:37,840 --> 00:15:39,160
Hello, China Customs.

331
00:15:39,160 --> 00:15:40,440
Please, this way for inspection.

332
00:15:40,520 --> 00:15:41,360
Officer,

333
00:15:41,480 --> 00:15:43,480
