334
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:44,560
We're running late.

335
00:15:44,560 --> 00:15:45,920
Don't worry, as long as you cooperate,

336
00:15:45,920 --> 00:15:46,800
it won't take long.

337
00:15:47,440 --> 00:15:47,880
Zhang.

338
00:15:47,880 --> 00:15:48,440
Over here.

339
00:15:48,480 --> 00:15:49,560
Larry and I will go now.

340
00:15:49,560 --> 00:15:50,880
You stay here
for the luggage inspection.

341
00:15:50,880 --> 00:15:52,320
Take a taxi and join us later.

342
00:15:52,320 --> 00:15:53,120
Got it.

343
00:15:53,720 --> 00:15:55,240
Sorry, rules require

344
00:15:55,520 --> 00:15:56,560
