345
00:15:56,560 --> 00:15:58,360
It's Larry's interview
after the championship today.

346
00:15:58,360 --> 00:16:00,000
You know how many people are waiting?

347
00:16:00,040 --> 00:16:00,960
Please calm down.

348
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,960
Please calm down and cooperate with us.

349
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,120
Calm down.

350
00:16:04,120 --> 00:16:05,160
Listen to me.

351
00:16:05,160 --> 00:16:06,560
Let's not fight.

352
00:16:06,560 --> 00:16:08,320
I'm also a fan of Larry.

353
00:16:08,440 --> 00:16:09,960
I'm also so happy seeing him

354
00:16:09,960 --> 00:16:10,800
with the trophy.

355
00:16:10,840 --> 00:16:12,320
I share your feelings.

356
00:16:12,320 --> 00:16:12,880
No photos.

357
00:16:12,880 --> 00:16:14,080
But here's the thing.

358
00:16:14,240 --> 00:16:15,200
This is the Customs.

359
00:16:15,400 --> 00:16:18,000
Customs has its rules.

360
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:20,360
You wouldn't want some trolls

361
00:16:20,360 --> 00:16:22,360
to attack and accuse Larry

362
00:16:22,360 --> 00:16:24,320
of not following customs rules, right?

363
00:16:24,520 --> 00:16:26,280
He is a public figure, right?

364
00:16:26,280 --> 00:16:27,920
Can't tarnish his image, right?

365
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:35,040
Let me handle this, okay?

366
00:16:35,040 --> 00:16:36,120
I'll handle it.

367
00:16:37,320 --> 00:16:38,040
Mr. Chen.

368
00:16:41,080 --> 00:16:42,560
Let him skip the line, okay?

369
00:16:42,680 --> 00:16:43,800
Make an exception.

370
00:16:44,440 --> 00:16:45,960
Make an exception, right?

371
00:16:45,960 --> 00:16:47,960
Yeah!

372
00:16:47,960 --> 00:16:49,600
Just be more understanding.

373
00:16:50,400 --> 00:16:51,840
I'm helping you, right?

374
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:52,720
Yes, you are.

375
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:54,000
Keep moving. Keep going.

376
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:55,400
Since I'm helping you,

377
00:16:55,400 --> 00:16:57,120
I hope you can also help me, okay?

378
00:16:57,120 --> 00:16:58,320
Okay.

379
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,040
Now, the fans

380
00:16:59,040 --> 00:17:00,560
