381
00:17:00,560 --> 00:17:01,160
Alright?

382
00:17:01,160 --> 00:17:02,000
Okay.

383
00:17:02,000 --> 00:17:03,440
Wait outside, okay?

384
00:17:04,800 --> 00:17:05,880
Thank you.

385
00:17:07,080 --> 00:17:08,800
Thanks for your cooperation.

386
00:17:09,240 --> 00:17:10,360
Thank you.

387
00:17:10,360 --> 00:17:11,000
Okay, Larry.

388
00:17:11,000 --> 00:17:11,920
This way, please.

389
00:17:16,560 --> 00:17:17,680
Here, this way.

390
00:17:22,840 --> 00:17:24,680
Please put your luggage
through the X-ray machine.

391
00:17:26,760 --> 00:17:27,440
Well, you see,

392
00:17:27,640 --> 00:17:28,800
I'm really a big fan.

393
00:17:28,800 --> 00:17:29,960
Could I have your autograph?

394
00:17:30,720 --> 00:17:31,320
Sure.

395
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:32,800
Thank you so much.

396
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:41,880
What's wrong?

397
00:17:42,400 --> 00:17:43,040
Nothing.

398
00:17:43,640 --> 00:17:46,280
One of us is a huge fan of you.

399
00:17:46,360 --> 00:17:49,000
I was signaling Chen to get him here.

400
00:17:49,720 --> 00:17:50,160
Seriously?

401
00:17:50,160 --> 00:17:51,800
Are your people always
this casual at work?

402
00:17:52,200 --> 00:17:53,560
Well, we've got an idol here.

403
00:17:54,080 --> 00:17:55,040
Oh, excuse me.

404
00:17:55,120 --> 00:17:57,120
This trophy needs
to go through the X-ray.

405
00:17:57,200 --> 00:17:58,040
Here, let me.

406
00:18:02,040 --> 00:18:03,760
