410
00:18:10,560 --> 00:18:12,200
This is only around one kilo.

411
00:18:12,560 --> 00:18:13,400
Step back!

412
00:18:14,320 --> 00:18:16,320
Cooperate with our inspection.

413
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:20,920
It's an international championship trophy.

414
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:22,840
Cause any damage to it,

415
00:18:23,400 --> 00:18:24,720
