419
00:18:29,880 --> 00:18:30,600
Didn't I?

420
00:18:37,640 --> 00:18:38,360
Never mind.

421
00:18:41,040 --> 00:18:42,120
You take care of the trophy.

422
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,040
I'll wait for you outside.

423
00:18:43,160 --> 00:18:43,720
Sure.

424
00:18:45,000 --> 00:18:46,520
Please cooperate
with customs inspection.

425
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:51,800
I've been cooperating,

426
00:18:52,200 --> 00:18:54,040
and you've been holding me up here

427
00:18:54,040 --> 00:18:55,280
with various excuses.

428
00:18:55,520 --> 00:18:57,600
So you competed in world-class events.

429
00:18:57,720 --> 00:18:59,040
Got some nerves of steel.

430
00:18:59,040 --> 00:19:00,800
Then cooperate with us one more time

431
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,200
in the inspection room.

432
00:19:03,720 --> 00:19:04,440
This way.

433
00:19:08,800 --> 00:19:09,360
Shihuo,

434
00:19:09,600 --> 00:19:10,920
