435
00:19:11,600 --> 00:19:12,120
This way.

436
00:19:12,120 --> 00:19:13,040
- This way. - Sorry.

437
00:19:16,360 --> 00:19:17,000
Larry!

438
00:19:17,280 --> 00:19:21,200
Larry!

439
00:19:21,320 --> 00:19:23,360
Larry!

440
00:19:25,040 --> 00:19:27,480
Larry has a livestream to attend!

441
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:38,360
This trophy didn't come easily, right?

442
00:19:38,520 --> 00:19:40,040
Quite prestigious, isn't it?

443
00:19:40,960 --> 00:19:41,960
Of course.

444
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:43,640
It was the World Elite Invitational.

445
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:45,960
Only the top 20 players in the world

446
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:46,840
could participate.

447
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:48,240
Officer,

448
00:19:48,600 --> 00:19:50,080
