449
00:19:50,200 --> 00:19:52,040
We really are running out of time.

450
00:19:52,800 --> 00:19:54,240
Relax. I'll be quick.

451
00:19:54,680 --> 00:19:55,160
Cong,

452
00:19:55,360 --> 00:19:56,120
