453
00:19:56,240 --> 00:19:56,720
Now.

454
00:19:57,440 --> 00:19:58,320
What do you want to do?

455
00:19:59,280 --> 00:20:00,200
Take it easy.

456
00:20:02,400 --> 00:20:03,200
What are you doing?

457
00:20:07,200 --> 00:20:08,000
Wait.

458
00:20:09,520 --> 00:20:10,880
What's this smell?

459
00:20:14,640 --> 00:20:16,480
A sourness typical of drugs.

460
00:20:17,840 --> 00:20:18,880
Drugs?

461
00:20:20,520 --> 00:20:21,360
Dayu.

462
00:20:21,800 --> 00:20:23,120
Get anti-smuggling guys here.

463
00:20:25,680 --> 00:20:27,000
You didn't know he's been using?

464
00:20:28,800 --> 00:20:30,480
I… I didn't.

465
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,120
Look at the scar on his palm.

466
00:20:34,240 --> 00:20:37,240
It's a burn scar left
by a heated glass tube

467
00:20:37,720 --> 00:20:40,280
when he was in a daze,

468
00:20:40,480 --> 00:20:41,600
with his senses dulled,

469
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:43,040
after using drugs.

470
00:20:43,880 --> 00:20:44,440
Right?

471
00:20:44,840 --> 00:20:45,960
I saw it before.

472
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,160
I thought it was

473
00:20:47,160 --> 00:20:48,760
from his mouse handling.

474
00:20:49,040 --> 00:20:49,960
Larry,

475
00:20:50,760 --> 00:20:52,520
how could you be so foolish?

476
00:20:52,720 --> 00:20:54,520
Why did you touch drugs?

477
00:20:54,520 --> 00:20:55,880
Mr. Chen, anti-smuggling men are here.

478
00:21:13,320 --> 00:21:14,520
Zheng, he's all yours.

479
00:21:29,880 --> 00:21:33,160
Larry!

480
00:21:33,160 --> 00:21:33,880
I'm here for you!

481
00:21:33,880 --> 00:21:35,640
Larry!

482
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:37,480
Are fans all this crazy now?

483
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:38,000
Larry!

484
00:21:38,000 --> 00:21:39,360
Those esports players

485
00:21:39,360 --> 00:21:41,520
are like movie or TV stars now.

486
00:21:41,800 --> 00:21:44,320
Those must have been his fans for years.

487
00:21:44,840 --> 00:21:46,280
Dayu is also like them.

488
00:21:46,280 --> 00:21:47,440
He could watch his competition videos

489
00:21:47,440 --> 00:21:48,560
for an entire afternoon.

490
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:51,960
Aren't you also

491
00:21:51,960 --> 00:21:53,680
one of this Larry's fans?

492
00:21:54,880 --> 00:21:56,440
I was just pretending to be.

493
00:21:56,760 --> 00:21:58,560
You told me to get a pen and paper.

494
00:21:58,560 --> 00:21:59,800
I figured you must

495
00:21:59,800 --> 00:22:01,480
want me to ask him for an autograph

496
00:22:01,760 --> 00:22:02,320
so you can check

497
00:22:02,320 --> 00:22:04,400
for any drug-use marks on his hands.

498
00:22:05,520 --> 00:22:07,640
Good, you're quite smart.

499
00:22:08,040 --> 00:22:09,120
Fan, let me.

500
00:22:09,240 --> 00:22:09,680
Here you are.

501
00:22:10,440 --> 00:22:10,880
Thank you.

502
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:14,400
Sir.

503
00:22:15,320 --> 00:22:16,920
How did he get your attention?

504
00:22:16,960 --> 00:22:19,520
Jiang Shihuo made me realize

505
00:22:19,520 --> 00:22:21,960
the stamp case was too easy

506
00:22:22,320 --> 00:22:23,320
and too small.

507
00:22:23,920 --> 00:22:26,240
It was likely just a diversion.

508
00:22:26,760 --> 00:22:29,280
So I thought the big one
was still to come.

509
00:22:29,680 --> 00:22:30,240
This way.

510
00:22:31,720 --> 00:22:33,160
Then I saw this champion.

511
00:22:33,800 --> 00:22:35,800
You'd think he'd be excited

512
00:22:35,800 --> 00:22:36,720
with his fans around.

513
00:22:36,720 --> 00:22:37,640
But him?

514
00:22:41,720 --> 00:22:43,760
He was holding that trophy tightly.

515
00:22:43,760 --> 00:22:45,480
It was a defensive posture.

516
00:22:47,720 --> 00:22:50,720
Also, the AC here is freezing.

517
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:52,040
He wasn't wearing much,

518
00:22:52,360 --> 00:22:53,680
yet he kept wiping his sweat.

519
00:22:53,680 --> 00:22:55,280
And he yawned frequently.

520
00:22:57,040 --> 00:22:58,840
With so many of them traveling together,

521
00:22:59,480 --> 00:23:00,880
he could easily go through unnoticed.

522
00:23:04,040 --> 00:23:05,080
Most importantly,

523
00:23:05,080 --> 00:23:06,680
you told me he was red-hot.

524
00:23:07,640 --> 00:23:08,480
It looks like he just

525
00:23:08,480 --> 00:23:10,720
got back from an overseas competition.

526
00:23:11,040 --> 00:23:12,400
He's red-hot now.

527
00:23:14,400 --> 00:23:16,600
It seems the doll provided
accurate intelligence.

528
00:23:16,840 --> 00:23:17,880
The thing is,

529
00:23:18,440 --> 00:23:20,240
why not just tell us directly?

530
00:23:21,560 --> 00:23:22,680
Yeah.

531
00:23:23,200 --> 00:23:24,080
Why not?

532
00:23:38,640 --> 00:23:40,080
Who is this man?

533
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:43,320
Chief of Passenger Inspection Section I,

534
00:23:43,640 --> 00:23:44,600
Chen Sanhe.

535
00:23:45,440 --> 00:23:46,880
He's the one who got Larry.

536
00:23:47,320 --> 00:23:49,760
You said nothing could go wrong.

537
00:23:49,760 --> 00:23:50,840
Who would know?

538
00:23:51,800 --> 00:23:54,600
Our stuff was sealed inside the trophy.

539
00:23:55,160 --> 00:23:57,160
Why would anyone check there?

540
00:24:01,120 --> 00:24:02,960
You go put this picture

541
00:24:03,600 --> 00:24:05,640
inside the locker
at the transaction site.

542
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:10,080
We shall also give this Mr. Chen

543
00:24:10,240 --> 00:24:11,400
a little reminder.

544
00:24:12,080 --> 00:24:13,560
Should we put a pause

545
00:24:14,120 --> 00:24:15,280
on our operations?

546
00:24:15,360 --> 00:24:16,280
We can't.

547
00:24:16,440 --> 00:24:18,000
The money has already been paid.

548
00:24:18,160 --> 00:24:19,840
We have to get the cargo in.

549
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:22,200
I don't think

550
00:24:22,400 --> 00:24:23,480
we'd always be this unlucky.

551
00:24:31,840 --> 00:24:32,760
This time,

552
00:24:34,720 --> 00:24:37,120
they just got lucky.

553
00:24:54,000 --> 00:24:57,400
[Self-service Locker]

554
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,240
[Press to Deposit]

555
00:24:58,280 --> 00:24:59,920
[Password Slip Here]
Please take the password slip.

556
00:24:59,920 --> 00:25:02,600
[Password Slip Here]
Please deposit in Locker 14.

557
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:05,400
Close the locker.

558
00:25:20,960 --> 00:25:23,640
Please retrieve from Locker 14.

559
00:25:23,880 --> 00:25:25,160
Close the locker.

560
00:25:36,320 --> 00:25:38,720
[Case Summary]
Last week, we seized

561
00:25:38,840 --> 00:25:40,480
[High-level Mule of an Esport Champion]
a drug smuggling case

562
00:25:40,480 --> 00:25:41,520
[Case Summary
High-level Mule of an Esport Champion]

563
00:25:41,520 --> 00:25:42,560
involving Larry,

564
00:25:42,760 --> 00:25:43,760
or Tan Xiaoming, an esports player.

565
00:25:44,120 --> 00:25:45,480
But on the day of the seizure,

566
00:25:46,000 --> 00:25:47,680
many of his fans were there,

567
00:25:47,960 --> 00:25:51,360
resulting in the immediate exposure
of the case.

568
00:25:51,800 --> 00:25:54,440
Following this, we must

569
00:25:54,920 --> 00:25:55,960
be really careful

570
00:25:56,640 --> 00:25:58,400
and prevent information leaks.

571
00:25:59,400 --> 00:26:01,400
As Tan is a world champion,

572
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:04,160
the case has drawn widespread attention,

573
00:26:04,480 --> 00:26:06,600
causing an extremely negative impact.

574
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,560
The Binhai Customs

575
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:10,200
immediately reported this situation

576
00:26:10,400 --> 00:26:12,200
to General Administration of Customs.

577
00:26:12,800 --> 00:26:14,880
The anti-smuggling investigation
has revealed

578
00:26:15,080 --> 00:26:18,080
Tan accidentally took some soft drugs

579
00:26:18,320 --> 00:26:19,760
at a party last year

580
00:26:19,760 --> 00:26:21,680
when he was abroad for a competition

581
00:26:21,840 --> 00:26:23,800
and gradually became addicted.

582
00:26:24,160 --> 00:26:25,040
When he was

583
00:26:25,160 --> 00:26:27,760
buying drugs at high prices
through a middleman in Binhai,

584
00:26:27,760 --> 00:26:29,760
he caught the attention
of a drug-smuggling ring

585
00:26:29,840 --> 00:26:32,160
and later became

586
00:26:32,440 --> 00:26:34,480
their high-level mule.

587
00:26:35,160 --> 00:26:36,320
And the reward was

588
00:26:37,120 --> 00:26:38,600
enough drugs for his own use.

589
00:26:39,000 --> 00:26:40,280
Tan confessed that

590
00:26:40,840 --> 00:26:41,680
the plan was

591
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:45,200
he would place the trophy drugs

592
00:26:45,200 --> 00:26:47,040
in a locker at this supermarket.

593
00:26:47,880 --> 00:26:49,200
As the case was exposed,

594
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:51,800
