Take it easy.

600
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:08,920
I've even received bullets before.

601
00:27:09,240 --> 00:27:10,640
It's okay. Please continue.

602
00:27:10,760 --> 00:27:11,280
Chen,

603
00:27:11,880 --> 00:27:13,520
