608
00:27:22,200 --> 00:27:24,200
It could be one of his fans

609
00:27:24,520 --> 00:27:25,720
or some other passenger.

610
00:27:26,080 --> 00:27:28,000
Anyway, this shows

611
00:27:28,120 --> 00:27:30,920
