612
00:27:30,920 --> 00:27:31,760
I see.

613
00:27:32,600 --> 00:27:34,760
They are so brazen, Chief.

614
00:27:35,160 --> 00:27:36,880
We had just seized their drugs,

615
00:27:37,040 --> 00:27:37,720
and they

616
00:27:37,840 --> 00:27:39,760
