617
00:27:40,600 --> 00:27:41,160
Sir!

618
00:27:42,240 --> 00:27:42,920
Yes.

619
00:27:43,040 --> 00:27:43,920
It's a woman.

620
00:27:46,480 --> 00:27:49,280
The red cross was drawn with lipstick.

621
00:27:49,360 --> 00:27:51,760
[Found in the Locker for the Trophy]
The shade could be 420.

622
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:53,680
The mark looks smooth, so it might be

623
00:27:53,680 --> 00:27:55,800
one of the Serafini Floral series,

624
00:27:55,960 --> 00:27:57,240
whose users are

625
00:27:57,240 --> 00:27:58,800
mostly women in their 40s.

626
00:27:59,520 --> 00:28:00,680
I have finished.

627
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:04,520
Very good.

628
00:28:04,840 --> 00:28:05,840
Which section are you from?

629
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:07,920
Jiang Shihuo
from Passenger Inspection Section I.

630
00:28:08,520 --> 00:28:09,360
One of us…

631
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:11,440
Sit down.

632
00:28:11,680 --> 00:28:12,120
Yes, sir.

633
00:28:13,160 --> 00:28:14,880
Jiang Shihuo is doing great.

634
00:28:15,040 --> 00:28:16,360
At least we know

635
00:28:16,360 --> 00:28:18,960
