636
00:28:18,960 --> 00:28:20,320
in this ring.

637
00:28:20,520 --> 00:28:21,560
[Chen Sanhe's Photo]
Besides this photo,

638
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:23,480
[Chen Sanhe's Photo]
we also found other things that day.

639
00:28:24,000 --> 00:28:25,640
[Dolls]

640
00:28:25,640 --> 00:28:26,800
[Dolls]
The doll on the left

641
00:28:27,120 --> 00:28:29,320
was delivered to us
on the day of Tan's case.

642
00:28:29,480 --> 00:28:30,600
The doll on the right

643
00:28:30,760 --> 00:28:32,080
was found in the locker.

644
00:28:32,560 --> 00:28:33,600
The note before

645
00:28:33,600 --> 00:28:34,920
helped us catch Tan.

646
00:28:35,080 --> 00:28:37,400
[Notes; May 7, Drugs]
This time in the locker,

647
00:28:37,760 --> 00:28:38,720
[Clown Mask: Found in the Locker]
besides the doll,

648
00:28:39,240 --> 00:28:40,760
[Clown Mask: Found in the Locker]
there was also a clown mask.

649
00:28:44,640 --> 00:28:45,920
Got any ideas?

650
00:28:46,360 --> 00:28:47,640
The doll last time

651
