654
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,560
Taunting? Warning?

655
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:56,280
We can't know for sure.

656
00:28:56,280 --> 00:28:59,040
It seems they were using incomplete

657
00:28:59,160 --> 00:29:01,440
and unclear messages to toy with us.

658
00:29:02,000 --> 00:29:03,840
It means

659
00:29:04,040 --> 00:29:05,560
their next move

660
00:29:05,560 --> 00:29:07,240
may have something to do with this mask.

661
00:29:07,400 --> 00:29:09,000
Then we can follow this lead

662
00:29:09,000 --> 00:29:09,920
and keep investigating

663
00:29:09,920 --> 00:29:11,760
until we get all these clowns.

664
00:29:11,880 --> 00:29:12,240
Right.

665
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,920
Zhang, pull up those two dolls.

666
00:29:13,920 --> 00:29:14,680
[Notes]

667
00:29:15,280 --> 00:29:16,280
[Dolls]
I looked up

668
00:29:16,280 --> 00:29:17,560
[Dolls]
the two dolls on the Internet.

669
00:29:17,840 --> 00:29:18,880
[Dolls]
Let's take a closer look.

670
00:29:18,880 --> 00:29:20,720
[Dolls]
These brooches

671
00:29:21,040 --> 00:29:23,160
