672
00:29:23,640 --> 00:29:26,880
They look like the scepter of Hermes,

673
00:29:27,080 --> 00:29:28,880
the God of Commerce,
in our customs emblem.

674
00:29:29,280 --> 00:29:31,320
So these people

675
00:29:31,400 --> 00:29:32,920
must have done their research,

676
00:29:32,920 --> 00:29:34,200
and they're quite ritualistic.

677
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,040
I have finished.

678
00:29:35,040 --> 00:29:36,360
[Dolls]

679
00:29:36,360 --> 00:29:37,600
[Dolls]
Besides the God of Commerce,

680
00:29:38,240 --> 00:29:39,200
[Dolls]
Hermes

681
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:41,080
[Dolls]
also represents the God of Thieves,

682
00:29:41,440 --> 00:29:43,040
protecting all illegal acts.

683
00:29:45,160 --> 00:29:48,200
Using his scepter as their symbol,

684
00:29:48,400 --> 00:29:49,320
