685
00:29:49,640 --> 00:29:50,880
makes some sense.

686
00:29:51,840 --> 00:29:55,280
Since they relate themselves to Hermes,

687
00:29:55,680 --> 00:29:57,280
let's use the letter E,

688
00:29:57,280 --> 00:29:59,480
