689
00:29:59,600 --> 00:30:00,960
to name them

690
00:30:01,000 --> 00:30:02,760
Group E.

691
00:30:03,080 --> 00:30:04,760
They are not gods.

692
00:30:05,640 --> 00:30:08,080
They are vipers lurking around,

693
00:30:08,680 --> 00:30:09,680
