695
00:30:12,840 --> 00:30:13,400
Therefore,

696
00:30:13,640 --> 00:30:15,520
we must catch them.

697
00:30:39,360 --> 00:30:41,160
This is the third doll we've received.

698
00:30:41,400 --> 00:30:43,080
[Perfume Is Poison]
And there's a note along with it.

699
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:43,880
[Perfume Is Poison]
Three words.

700
00:30:44,560 --> 00:30:46,320
[Perfume Is Poison]
Everyone, use your imagination.

701
00:30:47,120 --> 00:30:48,840
Why is 'perfume' in black

702
00:30:49,720 --> 00:30:51,160
and 'poison' in red?

703
00:30:52,240 --> 00:30:53,560
So many bottles of perfume.

704
00:30:54,000 --> 00:30:54,920
Is it possible

705
00:30:55,280 --> 00:30:56,680
[Perfume Is Poison]
there's a new type

706
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,160
[Note: Perfume Is Poison]
of liquid drug

707
00:30:58,480 --> 00:30:59,600
[Note: Perfume Is Poison]
that's harder to detect?

708
00:31:01,200 --> 00:31:02,000
Sir,

709
00:31:02,480 --> 00:31:04,040
please come with us
to the inspection room.

710
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:07,000
It seems they're using incomplete

711
00:31:07,080 --> 00:31:09,560
and unclear messages to toy with us.

712
00:31:09,920 --> 00:31:11,880
It means

713
00:31:12,000 --> 00:31:13,480
[Clown Mask: Found in the Locker]
their next move

714
00:31:13,480 --> 00:31:15,320
[Clown Mask: Found in the Locker]
may have something to do with this mask.

715
00:31:18,560 --> 00:31:19,920
[Face Mask]

716
00:31:21,720 --> 00:31:23,320
Miss, you've got too many face masks.

717
00:31:23,320 --> 00:31:24,320
They exceed the limit, I think.

718
00:31:57,920 --> 00:32:00,480
It's been a while
since we got the last doll.

719
00:32:01,000 --> 00:32:01,720
Have they

720
00:32:02,200 --> 00:32:03,520
backed off now?

721
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:08,920
It's basically all mules
we're bringing in.

722
00:32:09,400 --> 00:32:11,800
Can't get to the core members
of the ring.

723
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:15,440
But I am intrigued by that person

724
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,320
who placed the dolls.

725
00:32:17,040 --> 00:32:18,840
Though I can't figure out their purpose.

726
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:21,320
For example, "Perfume is poison."

727
00:32:21,840 --> 00:32:23,640
That's just too easy.

728
00:32:24,760 --> 00:32:25,480
Perhaps

729
00:32:25,760 --> 00:32:27,280
they think they're so clever.

730
00:32:28,200 --> 00:32:29,800
I don't think so.

731
00:32:32,440 --> 00:32:33,360
Then let's wait

732
00:32:33,800 --> 00:32:35,160
until they slip up.

733
00:32:37,440 --> 00:32:38,240
Shuo.

734
00:32:39,840 --> 00:32:40,840
Open another bottle.

735
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:43,360
You should stop.

736
00:32:43,800 --> 00:32:44,640
You're already drunk.

737
00:32:45,640 --> 00:32:48,160
Just do as you're told.

738
00:32:48,680 --> 00:32:50,200
I want to get drunk.

739
00:33:04,360 --> 00:33:05,280
That's it?

740
00:33:08,320 --> 00:33:09,160
That's enough.

741
00:33:20,720 --> 00:33:22,480
Using children to move cargo.

742
00:33:25,040 --> 00:33:26,520
Can you reconsider it?

743
00:33:35,720 --> 00:33:38,000
You wanna get on my nerves, too?

744
00:33:40,160 --> 00:33:42,920
You think I want to do that?

745
00:33:44,840 --> 00:33:46,320
I also want to bank some good deeds

746
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:48,000
for myself down the road.

747
00:33:49,000 --> 00:33:51,680
I'm gonna be a mother someday, alright?

748
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:55,560
But I have no other choice now.

749
00:33:58,600 --> 00:34:01,120
It's all because of that Chen Sanhe.

750
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:04,920
How many times has he seized my cargo?

751
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:08,720
And cargo is money.

752
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:12,000
I have to earn that money back.

753
00:34:12,360 --> 00:34:13,520
Otherwise,

754
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:15,560
