755
00:34:16,440 --> 00:34:18,880
How can I visit the Alps?

756
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:21,880
How can I have your child?

757
00:34:35,120 --> 00:34:36,680
Since we're using children,

758
00:34:38,280 --> 00:34:39,640
