759
00:34:44,080 --> 00:34:45,520
I'll get rid of Chen Sanhe.

760
00:34:46,640 --> 00:34:47,760
Have you lost your mind?

761
00:34:52,920 --> 00:34:54,440
We only do smuggling.

762
00:34:55,160 --> 00:34:56,200
We don't kill people.

763
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:59,120
I'm not that stupid.

764
00:35:01,960 --> 00:35:03,880
I just want to teach him a lesson.

765
00:35:05,400 --> 00:35:07,080
Put him in the hospital for a while.

766
00:35:09,560 --> 00:35:10,200
Sir,

767
00:35:12,320 --> 00:35:13,800
do you think one day

768
00:35:13,800 --> 00:35:15,400
all the criminals and smugglers

769
00:35:15,400 --> 00:35:17,440
in the world will just disappear?

770
00:35:22,200 --> 00:35:23,520
Humans have desires.

771
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:25,080
Desires result in selfish motives,

772
00:35:25,120 --> 00:35:27,080
which lead to secret agendas.

773
00:35:27,120 --> 00:35:28,880
And that would make people take risks.

774
00:35:30,360 --> 00:35:31,760
I wish for that day, too.

775
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:34,040
Then I could retire from this job

776
00:35:35,240 --> 00:35:36,200
and be free as a bird.

777
00:35:36,360 --> 00:35:37,560
Is that so hard?

778
00:35:38,360 --> 00:35:40,200
I am free as a bird now.

779
00:35:40,440 --> 00:35:41,040
Why not

780
00:35:41,560 --> 00:35:43,000
