781
00:35:43,320 --> 00:35:44,200
I'd love to,

782
00:35:44,640 --> 00:35:45,680
but on one condition.

783
00:35:46,880 --> 00:35:47,840
No smuggling in the world.

784
00:35:49,600 --> 00:35:51,320
Are you just making excuses

785
00:35:51,320 --> 00:35:52,200
for your workaholism?

786
00:35:52,240 --> 00:35:54,920
How could there
be no darkness in this world?

787
00:35:55,480 --> 00:35:57,600
Where there are days, there are nights.

788
00:35:57,880 --> 00:35:59,600
Where there is light, there are shadows.

789
00:36:01,040 --> 00:36:02,480
That's why

790
00:36:02,680 --> 00:36:04,840
Cong and I still have lots to do.

791
00:36:07,040 --> 00:36:08,760
Anyway, I'm always here.

792
00:36:09,640 --> 00:36:11,360
I don't have anything fancy.

793
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:14,560
But if you are tired or hungry,
just come.

794
00:36:15,440 --> 00:36:18,040
There are always noodles for you.

795
00:36:18,840 --> 00:36:19,600
I know.

796
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,000
This...

797
00:36:21,200 --> 00:36:23,800
Is this string about to break?

798
00:36:24,640 --> 00:36:25,600
Hold still.

799
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:26,400
Don't get burned.

800
00:36:34,680 --> 00:36:35,280
There.

801
00:36:36,840 --> 00:36:38,040
Don't worry. It's gonna be okay.

802
00:36:46,200 --> 00:36:47,240
More drinks?

803
00:36:52,280 --> 00:36:53,120
Want more food?

804
00:36:53,280 --> 00:36:53,800
No.

805
00:36:53,840 --> 00:36:54,360
I'm already full.

806
00:36:54,400 --> 00:36:55,480
We were just chatting.

807
00:37:15,360 --> 00:37:16,040
Hello?

808
00:37:17,160 --> 00:37:17,840
Hey.

809
00:37:19,720 --> 00:37:20,400
No, I'm good.

810
00:37:20,400 --> 00:37:21,840
I just had dinner with my mentor.

811
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:27,920
Well, is there anything you wanna eat?

812
00:37:28,200 --> 00:37:29,120
I'll bring it to you.

813
00:37:30,120 --> 00:37:31,240
Tell him to come eat here himself.

814
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:32,480
Why should we bring it to him?

815
00:37:35,840 --> 00:37:36,600
Alright, go ahead.

816
00:37:36,800 --> 00:37:37,800
I'll wait for you in the car.

817
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:40,640
We'll be your delivery guys.

818
00:37:42,680 --> 00:37:44,920
Hey, what do you want to eat?

819
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:48,880
Fei.

820
00:37:52,480 --> 00:37:54,000
Some food to go.

821
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:52,640
Thanks, Fei.

822
00:38:52,680 --> 00:38:53,760
Gotta go. Bye.

823
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,200
Sir!

824
00:39:14,760 --> 00:39:15,480
Sir!

825
00:39:15,920 --> 00:39:16,640
Sir!

826
00:39:17,120 --> 00:39:17,840
Sir!

827
00:39:27,040 --> 00:39:28,680
Sir?

828
00:39:30,240 --> 00:39:31,360
Come here.

829
00:39:39,600 --> 00:39:42,200
Easy, sir.

830
00:39:48,120 --> 00:39:48,920
Sir.

831
00:39:50,720 --> 00:39:51,440
Sir.

832
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:52,880
Sir.

833
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:54,920
Chen!

834
00:39:55,400 --> 00:39:57,200
Fei, call 120!

835
00:39:57,240 --> 00:39:59,560
Sir, hang in there.

836
00:39:59,560 --> 00:40:01,880
Just hang in there.

837
00:40:02,600 --> 00:40:03,160
Sir.

838
00:40:03,600 --> 00:40:04,200
Hello?

839
00:40:04,320 --> 00:40:04,720
Sir.

840
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:06,520
Is it the emergency center?

841
00:40:06,880 --> 00:40:09,440
I'm at Haixian Street,
Xunfeng District, Binhai City.

842
00:40:09,440 --> 00:40:10,880
There's a car accident here.

843
00:40:10,880 --> 00:40:11,400
Sir.

844
00:40:11,400 --> 00:40:12,760
Please come quickly!

845
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:25,640
Cong,

846
00:40:26,040 --> 00:40:27,040
you've been up all night.

847
00:40:27,640 --> 00:40:29,120
You need to rest now.

848
00:40:34,720 --> 00:40:37,120
Your mentor is awake now.

849
00:40:37,320 --> 00:40:38,720
The doctor said he's okay.

850
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:41,160
You should go home and get some rest.

851
00:40:41,760 --> 00:40:44,320
Cong, your mentor is injured now.

852
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:45,240
You have to stay strong.

853
00:40:45,280 --> 00:40:47,040
We need you in our work.

854
00:40:47,120 --> 00:40:49,320
The doctor said
there were more tests to run.

855
00:40:49,440 --> 00:40:52,360
Deng Hongxia and Wang Wenlei
are at the hospital.

856
00:40:52,680 --> 00:40:53,440
Now,

857
00:40:54,000 --> 00:40:54,720
