858
00:40:54,720 --> 00:40:55,520
Go home and sleep.

859
00:40:57,720 --> 00:40:58,440
- Chief. - Mr. Zhao.

860
00:40:58,440 --> 00:40:59,440
Have they got the offender?

861
00:41:00,320 --> 00:41:01,240
Not yet.

862
00:41:02,440 --> 00:41:04,720
Guo Cong, fortunately,
you weren't in the car.

863
00:41:05,360 --> 00:41:06,520
Do not panic.

864
00:41:06,720 --> 00:41:08,680
You should learn this from your mentor.

865
00:41:12,840 --> 00:41:14,840
At the scene, besides the suspect truck,

866
00:41:14,840 --> 00:41:15,880
there was another car.

867
00:41:15,880 --> 00:41:17,840
But I don't know
if it had anything to do

868
00:41:17,840 --> 00:41:18,840
with the car accident.

869
00:41:19,240 --> 00:41:20,600
But one thing is certain.

870
00:41:20,880 --> 00:41:23,400
The accident was Group E retaliating.

871
00:41:23,680 --> 00:41:25,040
I saw that doll

872
00:41:25,040 --> 00:41:25,920
with my own eyes at the scene.

873
00:41:26,320 --> 00:41:27,200
Probably.

874
00:41:27,800 --> 00:41:29,400
An investigation has been launched.

875
00:41:29,640 --> 00:41:31,840
You may get questioned in a few days.

876
00:41:35,680 --> 00:41:36,600
Take a look at this.

877
00:41:37,720 --> 00:41:38,920
Yes, this is the doll.

878
00:41:39,440 --> 00:41:41,120
Shen and I have examined it.

879
00:41:41,440 --> 00:41:42,400
Unlike previous ones,

880
00:41:42,600 --> 00:41:44,840
this doll carries no message.

881
00:41:44,880 --> 00:41:45,480
Yeah.

882
00:41:45,480 --> 00:41:46,720
So we believe

883
00:41:47,040 --> 00:41:49,480
this might just be a warning.

884
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,440
Guo Cong,

885
00:41:52,960 --> 00:41:54,680
your Section I has made

886
00:41:54,680 --> 00:41:56,200
the most seizures in these doll cases.

887
00:41:56,360 --> 00:41:58,920
Group E must have their eyes on you.

888
00:41:58,920 --> 00:41:59,440
So,

889
00:41:59,920 --> 00:42:01,720
you must be careful and stay safe.

890
00:42:01,920 --> 00:42:02,520
Yes, sir.

891
00:42:02,520 --> 00:42:04,960
Shen, take good care of them.

892
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:06,680
I will also send reinforcements

893
00:42:06,680 --> 00:42:07,760
to fully support Section I.

894
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,400
Yes, sir.

895
00:42:14,680 --> 00:42:15,600
Thank you.

896
00:42:35,240 --> 00:42:36,040
Cong,

897
00:42:37,040 --> 00:42:38,760
we all feel so sorry

898
00:42:39,800 --> 00:42:41,160
for what happened to your mentor.

899
00:42:42,080 --> 00:42:43,160
But no matter what,

900
00:42:43,640 --> 00:42:45,600
you can't bring your emotions into work.

901
00:42:46,520 --> 00:42:48,720
I believe your mentor
would expect the same.

902
00:42:52,160 --> 00:42:53,080
Got it, Deng.

903
00:42:57,640 --> 00:42:59,160
Hello, China Customs.

904
00:43:30,800 --> 00:43:37,360
♪There's a place of simple,
everyday warmth♪

905
00:43:38,280 --> 00:43:45,000
♪A door left open
for the wandering soul♪

906
00:43:45,920 --> 00:43:52,440
♪A humble table still warm with love♪

907
00:43:52,680 --> 00:43:56,320
♪After you've tasted every high and low♪

908
00:43:56,600 --> 00:44:00,240
♪Come home, I'll keep you warm♪

909
00:44:01,000 --> 00:44:07,680
♪Where the days begin and end♪

910
00:44:08,400 --> 00:44:15,320
♪A light still on for the ones
who've lost their way♪

911
00:44:16,120 --> 00:44:22,680
♪An embrace waiting just for you♪

912
00:44:22,960 --> 00:44:26,680
♪Through every passing season♪

913
00:44:26,800 --> 00:44:30,480
♪Even if you return with nothing at all♪

914
00:44:31,120 --> 00:44:34,600
♪Turn around and look♪

915
00:44:34,800 --> 00:44:38,600
♪That door's still open♪

916
00:44:38,800 --> 00:44:42,440
♪A light still burning♪

917
00:44:42,520 --> 00:44:46,240
♪Waiting there for you♪

918
00:44:46,400 --> 00:44:49,920
♪Turn around and look♪

919
00:44:50,160 --> 00:44:53,960
♪Someone's still waiting♪

920
00:44:54,160 --> 00:44:57,760
♪Watching the dusk settle in♪

921
00:44:57,840 --> 00:45:01,560
♪Waiting for the break of dawn♪

922
00:45:03,320 --> 00:45:06,960
♪It's always there♪
